Using new E2Kv7 ops for AES cipher (encrypt+decrypt).
Non-optimal: hack of generic implementation now.

1) Testing of raw speed

for m in aes-128-xts aes-256-xts aes-128-gcm aes-256-gcm \
         aes-192-gcm aes-128-ctr aes-256-ctr aes-192-ctr \
         aes-128-cbc aes-256-cbc aes-192-cbc
do
  openssl speed -evp $m 2>/dev/null | tail -1
done

